{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Great creativity. In times of need, we need great creativity."},{"time":5000,"text":"Discuss. Great creativity is astonishingly, absurdly, rationally, irrationally powerful."},{"time":13000,"text":"Great creativity can spread tolerance, champion freedom,"},{"time":17000,"text":"make education seem like a bright idea."},{"time":20000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":21000,"text":"Great creativity can turn a spotlight on deprivation,"},{"time":25000,"text":"or show that deprivation ain't necessarily so."},{"time":29000,"text":"Great creativity can make politicians electable,"},{"time":32000,"text":"or parties unelectable."},{"time":35000,"text":"It can make war seem like tragedy or farce."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"Creativity is the meme-maker that puts slogans on our t-shirts"},{"time":43000,"text":"and phrases on our lips."},{"time":45000,"text":"It's the pathfinder that shows us a simple road"},{"time":48000,"text":"through an impenetrable moral maze."},{"time":50000,"text":"Science is clever, but great creativity is something less knowable,"},{"time":55000,"text":"more magical. And now we need that magic."},{"time":58000,"text":"This is a time of need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"Our climate is changing quickly, too quickly."},{"time":62000,"text":"And great creativity is needed to do what it does so well:"},{"time":65000,"text":"to provoke us to think differently with dramatic creative statements."},{"time":69000,"text":"To tempt us to act differently"},{"time":71000,"text":"with delightful creative scraps."},{"time":74000,"text":"Here is one such scrap from an initiative I'm involved in"},{"time":77000,"text":"using creativity to inspire people to be greener."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"(Video) Man: You know, rather than drive today, I'm going to walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84000,"text":"Narrator: And so he walked, and as he walked he saw things."},{"time":88000,"text":"Strange and wonderful things he would not otherwise have seen."},{"time":92000,"text":"A deer with an itchy leg. A flying motorcycle."},{"time":95000,"text":"A father and daughter separated from a bicycle by a mysterious wall."},{"time":100000,"text":"And then he stopped. Walking in front of him was her."},{"time":105000,"text":"The woman who as a child had skipped with him through fields"},{"time":108000,"text":"and broken his heart."},{"time":109000,"text":"Sure, she had aged a little."},{"time":111000,"text":"In fact, she had aged a lot."},{"time":112000,"text":"But he felt all his old passion for her return."},{"time":115000,"text":"\"Ford,\" he called softly. For that was her name."},{"time":119000,"text":"\"Don't say another word, Gusty,\" she said,"},{"time":121000,"text":"for that was his name."},{"time":122000,"text":"\"I know a tent next to a caravan, exactly 300 yards from here."},{"time":127000,"text":"Let's go there and make love. In the tent.\""},{"time":130000,"text":"Ford undressed. She spread one leg, and then the other."},{"time":134000,"text":"Gusty entered her boldly and made love to her rhythmically"},{"time":138000,"text":"while she filmed him, because she was a keen amateur pornographer."},{"time":141000,"text":"The earth moved for both of them."},{"time":143000,"text":"And they lived together happily ever after."},{"time":146000,"text":"And all because he decided to walk that day."},{"time":152000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Andy Hobsbawm: We've got the science, we've had the debate."},{"time":165000,"text":"The moral imperative is on the table."},{"time":167000,"text":"Great creativity is needed to take it all,"},{"time":169000,"text":"make it simple and sharp."},{"time":171000,"text":"To make it connect. To make it make people want to act."},{"time":175000,"text":"So this is a call, a plea,"},{"time":177000,"text":"to the incredibly talented TED community."},{"time":179000,"text":"Let's get creative against climate change."},{"time":181000,"text":"And let's do it soon. Thank you."},{"time":183000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}